			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2472380">
									

<p>Well, the tale was written because I was unsantified that Maxwellists didn't do much in Hello World and aslo wasn't convinced that virtual cities are the way Maxwellism really works. So this is my interpretation of why they didn't react to the deaths. I just intend to build on the Maxwellist story :3</p>
<p>As for the fight… Well, there's my limited art ability :P At first there's only the picture in the middle but Athena commented that it seems comical, and I aslo find it a bit to abrupt. But after adding the two pictures, I did get feedback that it seems more comical from some… So well, I guess you can't satifiy everyone :P It's just that it's the only thing I can come up with.</p>
<p>And thanks for the read anyways :3</p>

