<p>As I've said on this before: I like this a lot better than the Hello World series. It takes much greater advantage of the massive possibilities of a virtual community, and expands the scopes of Maxwellism. The visuals aren't gimmicky, they're thematically appropriate and used tastefully, as well as being darn pretty to look at. Enthusiastically upvoted.</p>

